import React, { Component } from 'react';
import Input from './Input';
import TextArea from './TextArea';

export default class Form extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <form>
        <Input
          type="text"
          label="Nome"
          id="InputName"
          dataTest="name-input"
        />

        <TextArea
          label="Descrição da carta"
          id="descTextArea"
          dataTest="description-input"
        />

        <Input
          type="number"
          label="Atributo 1"
          id="descTextArea"
          dataTest="attr1-input"
        />

        <Input
          type="number"
          label="Atributo 2"
          id="descTextArea"
          dataTest="attr2-input"
        />

        <Input
          type="number"
          label="Atributo 3"
          id="descTextArea"
          dataTest="attr3-input"
        />
      </form>
    );
  }
}
